leading_list
['/*+Leading(an rt)*/']
pg plan: 0.031113 pg run: 0.007794
totalTime: 7.794
mcts: 2.075835943222046 plan gen: 0.031113 MPHE: 0.010725021362304688 hinter latency: 0.007794
SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Home Entertainment'
AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
'marvel-comics',
'based-on-novel',
'soothsayer')
AND t.production_year > 2009;
[['PG'], [7.794]]
0.0311 2.0758 0.0311 0.0107 0.0078 0.0078 1.0000

       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Home Entertainment'
AND k.keyword IN ('marvel-comics',
'fight',
'violence',
'mission')
AND t.production_year > 2009;

     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id

  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Animation'

'female-nudity',
'based-on-comic',
'banquet')

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Animation'
AND k.keyword IN ('hand-to-hand-combat',
'second-part',
'based-on-novel',
'kung-fu-master')
AND t.production_year > 2009;

FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Animation'
AND k.keyword IN ('based-on-novel',
'blood',
'superhero',
'kung-fu')
AND t.production_year > 2009;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Animation'
AND k.keyword IN ('superhero',
'sequel',
'sequel',
'father-son-relationship')
AND t.production_year > 2008;

totalTime: 3062.9090000000006
mcts: 3.968017816543579 plan gen: 0.03294 MPHE: 0.008890867233276367 hinter latency: 0.008773999999999999
SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'NBC Universal Television'
AND k.keyword IN ('violence',
'superhero',
'blood',
'preparation')
AND t.production_year > 2008;

     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,

     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t

                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')

       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')

  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Animation'

'blood',
'tv-special',

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Animation'
AND k.keyword IN ('gore',
'magnet',
'based-on-comic',
'restaurant')
AND t.production_year > 2008;
[['PG'], [10.207]]

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'NBC Universal Television'
AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
'fight',
'violence',
'tough-guy')
AND t.production_year > 2008;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'NBC Universal Television'
AND k.keyword IN ('violence',
'tv-special',
'based-on-comic',
'host')
AND t.production_year > 2008;

     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Home Entertainment'
AND k.keyword IN ('sequel',
'magnet',
'superhero',
'mother-son-relationship')
AND t.production_year > 2009;

       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id

       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'NBC Universal Television'
AND k.keyword IN ('claw',
'laser',
'tv-special',
'martial-artist')
AND t.production_year > 2008;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id

       MIN(t.title) AS hero_movie
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('martial-arts',
'murder',
'superhero',
'tv-special',
'marvel-comics',
'superhero',
'second-part',
'laser')
AND t.production_year > 1999;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'NBC Universal Television'
AND k.keyword IN ('marvel-comics',
'tv-special',
'superhero',
'tough-guy')
AND t.production_year > 2008;
[['PG'], [8.26]]
10.5989 1689.7228 10.8729 3.8988 298.8060 498.3910 1.6679

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
'(executive producer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(as Anya)')
AND n.name like '%Kop,%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000  AND 2009;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Animation'
AND k.keyword IN ('laser',
'superhero',
'fight',
'hand-to-hand-combat')
AND t.production_year > 2008;

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id

       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')

       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')

'(writer)',

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda

     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,

                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'

       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')

  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id

     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,

     role_type AS rt,

       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')

  AND rt.id = ci.role_id

  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id

     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t

SQL : SELECT MIN(k.keyword) AS movie_keyword,
       MIN(n.name) AS actor_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS hero_movie
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id

'superhero',
'tv-special',

'superhero',
'marvel-comics',
'female-nudity',
'violence')
AND t.production_year > 1997;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Home Entertainment'
AND k.keyword IN ('sequel',
'death',
'character-name-in-title',
'presumed-dead')
AND t.production_year > 2009;

totalTime: 1159716.0690000013

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(executive producer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(voice)',
'(archive footage)')
AND n.name like '%Madonna%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1997  AND 2011;
[['PG'], [8.142]]

SQL : SELECT MIN(k.keyword) AS movie_keyword,
       MIN(n.name) AS actor_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS hero_movie
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id

'murder-in-title',
'second-part',
'hand-to-hand-combat',
'marvel-cinematic-universe',
'female-nudity',
'claw',
'second-part')
AND t.production_year > 2000;

SQL : SELECT MIN(kt.kind) AS movie_kind,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id

  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.status_id
  AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
  AND kt.kind IN ('movie')
  AND t.production_year > 1999;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'NBC Universal Television'
AND k.keyword IN ('marvel-comics',
'web',
'tv-special',
'tough-girl')
AND t.production_year > 2008;

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id

  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id

       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(producer)',
'(archive footage)')
AND n.name like '%Anna%'

SQL : SELECT MIN(kt.kind) AS movie_kind,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.status_id
  AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
  AND kt.kind IN ('movie')
  AND t.production_year > 2001;
[['/*+Leading(cc cct1)*/'], [8317.837]]

SQL : SELECT MIN(k.keyword) AS movie_keyword,
       MIN(n.name) AS actor_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS hero_movie
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('fight',
'marvel-comics',
'murder',
'superhero',
'claw',
'violence',
'sequel',
'hospital')
AND t.production_year > 2010;

SQL : SELECT MIN(kt.kind) AS movie_kind,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.status_id
  AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
  AND kt.kind IN ('movie')
  AND t.production_year > 1997;

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(executive producer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(writer)',
'(as Mayte Jannell Garcia)')
AND n.name like '%Mayte%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1994  AND 2006;

SQL : SELECT MIN(k.keyword) AS movie_keyword,
       MIN(n.name) AS actor_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS hero_movie
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE k.id = mk.keyword_id

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,

     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,

                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')

       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')

  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id

SQL : SELECT MIN(kt.kind) AS movie_kind,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.status_id
  AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
  AND kt.kind IN ('movie')
  AND t.production_year > 1996;

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(voice)',
'(segment ''The Science of Sleep'')')
AND n.name like '%Lesley%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2006  AND 2013;

     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.status_id
  AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
  AND kt.kind IN ('movie')
  AND t.production_year > 2009;

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS western_dark_production
FROM info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE it1.info = 'countries'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND (t.title LIKE '%murder%'
       OR t.title LIKE '%Murder%'
       OR t.title LIKE '%Mord%')
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('superhero',
'newspaper-headline')
AND kt.kind = 'episode'
AND mi.info IN ('Denish',
'Norwegian',
'Bulgaria',
'Denmark',
'American',
'America',
'Danish',
'Sweden',
'English',
'UK')
AND mi_idx.info > '10'

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda

     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id

  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'NBC Universal Television'

'violence',

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS western_dark_production

     info_type AS it2,

     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t

  AND t.id = mi.movie_id

SQL : SELECT MIN(kt.kind) AS movie_kind,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t

  AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL

       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')

  AND cct1.id = cc.status_id
  AND cn.country_code = '[us]'

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS western_dark_production
FROM info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE it1.info = 'countries'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND (t.title LIKE '%murder%'
       OR t.title LIKE '%Murder%'
       OR t.title LIKE '%Mord%')
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('based-on-comic',
'faking-own-death')
AND kt.kind = 'episode'
AND mi.info IN ('Denish',
'American',
'Danish',
'Norwegian',
'Germany',
'America',
'English',
'Swedish',
'Norway',
'USA')
AND mi_idx.info > '6.5'
AND t.production_year > 1969;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'NBC Universal Television'
AND k.keyword IN ('second-part',
'violence',
'hospital',
'comic-hero')
AND t.production_year > 2008;
[['PG'], [11.77]]

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS western_dark_production
FROM info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE it1.info = 'countries'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND (t.title LIKE '%murder%'
       OR t.title LIKE '%Murder%'
       OR t.title LIKE '%Mord%')
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('based-on-comic',
'based-on-novel')
AND kt.kind = 'episode'
AND mi.info IN ('Bulgaria',
'Denmark',
'Norwegian',
'Germany',
'English',
'Swedish',
'American',
'Sweden',
'USA',
'UK')
AND mi_idx.info > '10'
AND t.production_year > 1999;

SQL : SELECT MIN(kt.kind) AS movie_kind,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id

  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.status_id
  AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
  AND kt.kind IN ('movie')
  AND t.production_year > 1995;

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(uncredited)',
'(voice)',

SQL : SELECT MIN(kt.kind) AS movie_kind,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.status_id
  AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
  AND kt.kind IN ('movie')
  AND t.production_year > 1999;

     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,

SQL : SELECT MIN(k.keyword) AS movie_keyword,
       MIN(n.name) AS actor_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS hero_movie
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('marvel-cinematic-universe',
'10,000-mile-club',
'sequel',
'superhero',
'female-nudity',
'blood',
'murder',
'fight')
AND t.production_year > 1999;

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS western_dark_production
FROM info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE it1.info = 'countries'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id

       OR t.title LIKE '%Mord%')

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Animation'
AND k.keyword IN ('female-nudity',
'blood',
'murder-in-title',
'chop-socky')
AND t.production_year > 2009;

SQL : SELECT MIN(kt.kind) AS movie_kind,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t

  AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'

       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
'(voice)',
'(executive producer)',
'(uncredited)')
AND n.name like '%Bruno,%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2000  AND 2006;

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS western_dark_production
FROM info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE it1.info = 'countries'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id

       OR t.title LIKE '%Murder%'
       OR t.title LIKE '%Mord%')
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id

'maid')

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS western_dark_production
FROM info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE it1.info = 'countries'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id

'remake')

'American',

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id

  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id

       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')

       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id

'(producer)',

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS western_dark_production
FROM info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE it1.info = 'countries'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND (t.title LIKE '%murder%'
       OR t.title LIKE '%Murder%'
       OR t.title LIKE '%Mord%')
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('sequel',
'manic-laughter')
AND kt.kind = 'episode'
AND mi.info IN ('Germany',
'Bulgaria',
'Norway',
'Norwegian',
'German',
'America',
'English',
'Swedish',
'Danish',
'UK')
AND mi_idx.info > '6.2'

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(producer)',
'(writer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(as Vendela Kirsebom)')
AND n.name like '%Kirsebom%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2004  AND 2013;

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,

     movie_companies AS mc,

  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id

       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')

       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')

       MIN(t.title) AS western_follow_up
FROM company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.info IN ('Bulgaria',
'Denmark',
'Denish',
'English',
'German',
'Germany',
'Sweden',
'American',
'Swedish')
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1995  AND 2013;
[['PG'], [9.573]]

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(producer)',
'(voice)',
'(writer)',
'(as Terri Colombino)')
AND n.name like '%Conn,%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1997  AND 2006;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Home Entertainment'
AND k.keyword IN ('sequel',
'second-part',
'martial-arts',
'hope')
AND t.production_year > 2009;

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS western_dark_production
FROM info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE it1.info = 'countries'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND (t.title LIKE '%murder%'
       OR t.title LIKE '%Murder%'
       OR t.title LIKE '%Mord%')
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('murder',
'flashback')
AND kt.kind = 'episode'
AND mi.info IN ('Sweden',
'Norwegian',
'USA',
'Germany',
'English',
'Bulgaria',
'Denmark',
'Denish',
'American',
'USA')
AND mi_idx.info > '6.4'
AND t.production_year > 2009;

SQL : SELECT MIN(kt.kind) AS movie_kind,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS western_dark_production
FROM info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE it1.info = 'countries'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND (t.title LIKE '%murder%'
       OR t.title LIKE '%Murder%'
       OR t.title LIKE '%Mord%')
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('based-on-comic',
'interracial-marriage')
AND kt.kind = 'episode'
AND mi.info IN ('Danish',
'American',
'Sweden',
'Norway',
'USA',
'Swedish',
'Norwegian',
'Denmark',
'Bulgaria',
'USA')
AND mi_idx.info > '10'

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL

       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')

  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'

  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id

  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id

  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'

'fight',
'blood',
'panda')
AND t.production_year > 2008;

       MIN(t.title) AS western_follow_up
FROM company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.info IN ('Germany',
'America',
'Danish',
'American',
'Sweden',
'USA',
'Denish',
'Denmark',
'German')
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1998  AND 2000;
[['PG'], [8.668]]

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Animation'
AND k.keyword IN ('laser',
'superhero',
'fight',
'hand-to-hand-combat')
AND t.production_year > 2008;
[['PG'], [10.911]]

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(executive producer)',
'(writer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(as Terri Colombino)')
AND n.name like '%Conn,%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2002  AND 2008;

SQL : SELECT MIN(kt.kind) AS movie_kind,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id

     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(executive producer)',
'(voice)',
'(writer)',
'(segment ''The Race For The Electric Car'')')
AND n.name like '%Stahl,%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1998  AND 2011;

     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,

     role_type AS rt,

  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id

  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id

  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS western_dark_production
FROM info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE it1.info = 'countries'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND (t.title LIKE '%murder%'
       OR t.title LIKE '%Murder%'
       OR t.title LIKE '%Mord%')
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('marvel-comics',
'ruins')
AND kt.kind = 'episode'
AND mi.info IN ('Norwegian',
'Sweden',
'Bulgaria',
'English',
'Norway',
'German',
'Germany',
'Danish',
'Denmark',
'UK')
AND mi_idx.info > '8'
AND t.production_year > 1999;

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(uncredited)',
'(voice)',
'(producer)',
'(as Kimberly) (credit only)')
AND n.name like '%Kimberly%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1994  AND 2006;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'

SQL : SELECT MIN(kt.kind) AS movie_kind,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.status_id
  AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
  AND kt.kind IN ('movie')
  AND t.production_year > 1996;

     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.status_id
  AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
  AND kt.kind IN ('movie')
  AND t.production_year > 1994;
[['/*+Leading(cc cct1)*/'], [8339.165]]

     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,

     role_type AS rt,

       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
'(writer)',
'(executive producer)',
'(as Anya)')
AND n.name like '%Kop,%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1995  AND 2012;
