  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id

       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(producer)',
'(voice)',
'(uncredited)',
'(as Anya)')
AND n.name like '%Kop,%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1994  AND 2006;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Home Entertainment'
AND k.keyword IN ('marvel-comics',
'marvel-cinematic-universe',
'based-on-comic',
'mission')
AND t.production_year > 2009;

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS western_dark_production
FROM info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE it1.info = 'countries'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id

SQL : SELECT MIN(kt.kind) AS movie_kind,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie

     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,

     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t

       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')

  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.status_id
  AND cn.country_code = '[us]'

       MIN(t.title) AS hero_movie
FROM cast_info AS ci,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('sequel',
'superhero',
'tv-special',
'based-on-comic',
'superhero',
'marvel-comics',
'female-nudity',
'violence')
AND t.production_year > 1997;
[['PG'], [4333.131]]

SQL : SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS company_name,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS western_follow_up
FROM company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.info IN ('American',
'USA',
'Norway',
'Bulgaria',
'Swedish',
'German',
'Denmark',
'Danish',
'America')
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2001  AND 2010;
[['PG'], [7.831]]

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS western_dark_production
FROM info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE it1.info = 'countries'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND (t.title LIKE '%murder%'
       OR t.title LIKE '%Murder%'
       OR t.title LIKE '%Mord%')
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('based-on-comic',
'based-on-novel')
AND kt.kind = 'episode'
AND mi.info IN ('Bulgaria',
'Denmark',
'Norwegian',
'Germany',
'English',
'Swedish',
'American',
'Sweden',
'USA',
'UK')
AND mi_idx.info > '10'
AND t.production_year > 1999;
[['PG'], [2191.276]]

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Animation'
AND k.keyword IN ('female-nudity',
'blood',
'murder-in-title',
'chop-socky')
AND t.production_year > 2009;

SQL : SELECT MIN(kt.kind) AS movie_kind,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.status_id
  AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
  AND kt.kind IN ('movie')
  AND t.production_year > 2002;

     cast_info AS ci,

     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Animation'
AND k.keyword IN ('web',
'blood',
'superhero',
'chop-socky')
AND t.production_year > 2008;

SQL : SELECT MIN(kt.kind) AS movie_kind,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id

       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '7.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id

  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('based-on-comic',
'magnet',

SQL : SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS company_name,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS western_follow_up
FROM company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.info IN ('Norwegian',
'America',
'Norway',
'Danish',
'American',
'Denish',
'Denmark',
'Germany',
'USA')
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1994  AND 2003;

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(voice)',
'(segment ''The Science of Sleep'')')
AND n.name like '%Lesley%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 2006  AND 2013;

  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id

  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id

  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')

       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(executive producer)',
'(voice)',

AND n.name like '%Fequiere,%'

SQL : SELECT MIN(kt.kind) AS movie_kind,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie

     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,

     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t

  AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'

  AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '7.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('sequel',
'fight',
'based-on-comic',
'marvel-comics',

'tv-special',

'murder',

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
'(writer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(voice)')
AND n.name like '%Kavner,%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1997  AND 2006;

SQL : SELECT MIN(kt.kind) AS movie_kind,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id

  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id

  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.status_id
  AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
  AND kt.kind IN ('movie')
  AND t.production_year > 2000;

     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '7.0'

  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id

  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('second-part',
'marvel-cinematic-universe',
'marvel-comics',

SQL : SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS company_name,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS western_follow_up
FROM company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.info IN ('Germany',
'Denmark',
'German',
'Norwegian',
'Norway',
'Danish',
'American',
'Sweden',
'USA')
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1994  AND 2008;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'NBC Universal Television'
AND k.keyword IN ('blood',
'violence',
'female-nudity',
'comic-hero')
AND t.production_year > 2008;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '7.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('violence',
'blood',
'fight',
'fight',
'based-on-novel',
'marvel-comics',
'murder',
'based-on-comic',
'fight',
'marvel-comics')
AND t.production_year > 2003;

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(executive producer)',
'(writer)',
'(producer)',
'(as Allison) (credit only)')
AND n.name like '%Allison%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1996  AND 2012;

     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '7.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('laser',
'based-on-comic',
'tv-special',
'tv-special',

'hand-to-hand-combat',
'blood',
'violence',

SQL : SELECT MIN(kt.kind) AS movie_kind,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'NBC Universal Television'
AND k.keyword IN ('violence',
'laser',
'fight',
'cooking')
AND t.production_year > 2008;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '7.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('blood',
'death',
'fight',
'sequel',
'marvel-comics',
'superhero',
'based-on-comic',
'laser',
'magnet',
'sequel')
AND t.production_year > 2001;

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(uncredited)',
'(writer)',
'(producer)',
'(as Fatima)')
AND n.name like '%Fatima%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1998  AND 2008;

SQL : SELECT MIN(cn.name) AS company_name,
       MIN(lt.link) AS link_type,
       MIN(t.title) AS western_follow_up
FROM company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     keyword AS k,
     link_type AS lt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     movie_link AS ml,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code !='[pl]'
  AND (cn.name LIKE '%Film%'
       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')
  AND ct.kind ='production companies'
  AND k.keyword ='sequel'
  AND lt.link LIKE '%follow%'
  AND mc.note IS NULL
  AND lt.id = ml.link_type_id
  AND ml.movie_id = t.id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND mc.company_type_id = ct.id
  AND mc.company_id = cn.id
  AND mi.movie_id = t.id
  AND ml.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND ml.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.info IN ('Denmark',
'Bulgaria',
'Norway',
'German',
'English',
'Sweden',
'Danish',
'Denish',
'America')
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1999  AND 2013;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,

     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,

     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t

  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id

  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id

     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'

       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,

     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL

       MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie

     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'NBC Universal Television'

'based-on-comic',
'father-son-relationship')

     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,

  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id

  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id

pg plan: 0.034844 pg run: 15.596466

mcts: 3.5724759101867676 plan gen: 0.034844 MPHE: 0.00781702995300293 hinter latency: 15.596466
SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '7.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('magnet',
'marvel-comics',
'tv-special',
'web',
'murder-in-title',
'laser',
'hand-to-hand-combat',
'female-nudity',
'superhero',
'murder-in-title')
AND t.production_year > 2001;
[['PG'], [15596.466]]

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(t.title) AS western_dark_production
FROM info_type AS it1,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE it1.info = 'countries'
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND (t.title LIKE '%murder%'
       OR t.title LIKE '%Murder%'
       OR t.title LIKE '%Mord%')
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('claw',
'rosary')
AND kt.kind = 'episode'
AND mi.info IN ('USA',
'English',
'Swedish',
'Denmark',
'Danish',
'Norway',
'Denish',
'America',
'Sweden',
'Malta')
AND mi_idx.info > '6.5'
AND t.production_year > 2008;

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
'(voice)',
'(executive producer)',
'(archive footage)')
AND n.name like '%Madonna%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1999  AND 2010;
[['PG'], [10.531]]

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Home Entertainment'
AND k.keyword IN ('based-on-comic',
'murder',
'tv-special',
'hand-to-hand-combat')
AND t.production_year > 2009;

SQL : SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS release_date,
       MIN(miidx.info) AS rating,

     info_type AS it,
     info_type AS it2,
     kind_type AS kt,

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(writer)',
'(voice)',
'(executive producer)',
'(as Chaunte Schuler)')
AND n.name like '%Schuler%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1999  AND 2013;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS voiced_char_name,
       MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress_name,
       MIN(t.title) AS kung_fu_panda
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE ci.note IN ('(voice)',
                  '(voice: Japanese version)',
                  '(voice) (uncredited)',
                  '(voice: English version)')
  AND cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%201%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%201%')
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND n.name LIKE '%An%'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND t.title LIKE 'Kung Fu Panda%'
  AND cn.name = 'DreamWorks Animation'
AND k.keyword IN ('tv-special',
'violence',
'character-name-in-title',
'female-martial-artist')
AND t.production_year > 2008;

     title AS t

       OR cn.name LIKE '%Warner%')

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(executive producer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(voice)',
'(voice)')
AND n.name like '%Cartwright,%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1995  AND 2007;

       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')

       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')

SQL : SELECT MIN(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
       MIN(t.title) AS voiced_movie
FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,
     title AS t
WHERE cn.country_code ='[us]'
  AND it.info = 'release dates'
  AND mc.note IS NOT NULL
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND n.gender ='f'
  AND rt.role ='actress'
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND it.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND rt.id = ci.role_id
  AND n.id = an.person_id
  AND ci.person_id = an.person_id
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'Japan:%200%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:%200%')
  AND (mc.note LIKE '%(USA)%'
       OR mc.note LIKE '%(worldwide)%')
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND ci.note IN ('(voice)',
'(producer)',
'(uncredited)',
'(as Terri Colombino)')
AND n.name like '%Terri%'
AND t.production_year BETWEEN 1997  AND 2011;

       MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'complete+verified'
  AND it1.info = 'release dates'
  AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mi.movie_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = mc.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = mc.movie_id
  AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mc.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id
  AND cn.id = mc.company_id
  AND ct.id = mc.company_type_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.status_id
  AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
  AND kt.kind IN ('movie')
  AND t.production_year > 2005;

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'
  AND mi_idx.info > '7.0'
  AND kt.id = t.kind_id
  AND t.id = mk.movie_id
  AND t.id = ci.movie_id
  AND t.id = cc.movie_id
  AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = ci.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id
  AND k.keyword IN ('based-on-comic',
'superhero',
'10,000-mile-club',
'based-on-comic',
'based-on-novel',
'fight',
'violence',
'sequel',
'based-on-comic',
'web')
AND t.production_year > 1999;

FROM aka_name AS an,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     company_name AS cn,
     info_type AS it,
     keyword AS k,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     role_type AS rt,

SQL : SELECT MIN(chn.name) AS character_name,
       MIN(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
       MIN(n.name) AS playing_actor,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_hero_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     comp_cast_type AS cct2,
     char_name AS chn,
     cast_info AS ci,
     info_type AS it2,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_info_idx AS mi_idx,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     name AS n,
     title AS t
WHERE cct1.kind = 'cast'
  AND cct2.kind LIKE '%complete%'
  AND chn.name IS NOT NULL
  AND (chn.name LIKE '%man%'
       OR chn.name LIKE '%Man%')
  AND it2.info = 'rating'
  AND kt.kind = 'movie'

  AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id
  AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND cc.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id
  AND chn.id = ci.person_role_id
  AND n.id = ci.person_id
  AND k.id = mk.keyword_id
  AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id
  AND cct2.id = cc.status_id
  AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id

'murder',
'murder',
'based-on-novel',

SQL : SELECT MIN(kt.kind) AS movie_kind,
       MIN(t.title) AS complete_us_internet_movie
FROM complete_cast AS cc,
     comp_cast_type AS cct1,
     company_name AS cn,
     company_type AS ct,
     info_type AS it1,
     keyword AS k,
     kind_type AS kt,
     movie_companies AS mc,
     movie_info AS mi,
     movie_keyword AS mk,
     title AS t

  AND mi.note LIKE '%internet%'
  AND mi.info IS NOT NULL
  AND (mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 199%'
       OR mi.info LIKE 'USA:% 200%')

  AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
